# Micro SaaS Ideas

> Small-scale, niche-focused software-as-a-service opportunities aligned with existing skills.

---

## Why Micro SaaS?

**Market Size:** Gartner projects the SaaS market to hit $344 billion by 2028, growing at 13% CAGR.

**Why It Works for Solo Developers:**
- Many hit $5K-50K+ MRR with 1-3 person teams
- Low startup costs (often <$5K to MVP)
- Subscription model = predictable recurring revenue
- Can be built alongside consulting income

> Source: [Superframeworks](https://superframeworks.com/blog/best-micro-saas-ideas), [Microns](https://www.microns.io/blog/best-micro-saas-ideas)

---

## Idea 1: Golf League Management Platform (LazyGolf Core)

**Already in development as [[Ventures/LazyGolf]] platform vertical**

But consider these **spinoff opportunities:**

### A. White-Label League Software

**Concept:** License the LazyGolf league management core to other golf-adjacent businesses (courses, clubs, corporate event organizers).

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High |
| Effort | Medium (core already being built) |
| Revenue | $99-499/mo per client |
| Moat | First to market with modern UX |

**Target Customers:**
- Golf courses wanting branded league management
- Corporate HR running golf outings
- Bar/restaurant leagues
- Charity tournament organizers

**Pricing Model:**
| Tier | Price | Features |
|------|-------|----------|
| Starter | $99/mo | 1 league, basic scoring, 50 members |
| Pro | $249/mo | 5 leagues, advanced stats, 200 members |
| Enterprise | $499/mo | Unlimited, white-label, API access |

### B. Golf Betting/Skins Calculator

**Concept:** Standalone app for calculating skins, nassau bets, wolf, and other side-game payouts automatically.

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High (validated pain point) |
| Effort | Low (2-4 weeks to MVP) |
| Revenue | $4.99/mo or $29.99/year |
| Moat | Low - execution and UX dependent |

**Why This Works:**
- Golfers do complex mental math on every hole
- Existing apps are clunky or non-existent
- Perfect upsell from LazyGolf platform
- Could integrate with Apple Watch

**Features:**
- [ ] Nassau calculator (front 9, back 9, overall)
- [ ] Skins game tracking with carryovers
- [ ] Wolf game management
- [ ] Automatic settlement suggestions
- [ ] Venmo/PayPal integration links

