## Idea 2: AI Content Tools for Niche Industries

**Market Context:** The AI content tool market is exploding. FounderPal reached ~$10K MRR within 6 months by targeting entrepreneurs specifically.

> Source: [Rapid Developers](https://www.rapidevelopers.com/blog/micro-saas-ideas-for-solopreneurs-2025)

### A. Golf Content Generator

**Concept:** AI-powered tool for golf courses, pro shops, and golf influencers to generate marketing content.

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | Medium-High |
| Effort | Medium (4-8 weeks) |
| Revenue | $19-49/mo |
| Moat | Niche focus + golf-specific prompts |

**Content Types:**
- Course condition updates
- Pro tip posts
- Tournament announcements
- Email newsletter drafts
- Social media captions
- Equipment review templates

**Why Not Just ChatGPT?**
- Pre-built templates for golf-specific content
- Brand voice training
- Image generation with golf context
- Scheduling integration

### B. Real Estate Listing Description Generator

**Concept:** AI tool specifically for realtors to generate property descriptions, social posts, and email campaigns.

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High (large market, proven pain) |
| Effort | Medium |
| Revenue | $29-79/mo |
| Moat | MLS integrations, realtor-specific templates |

**Why Real Estate:**
- Realtors are time-pressed and write tons of content
- Average agent lists 10-15 properties/year
- Each listing needs descriptions for MLS, Zillow, social, email
- Competitors exist but are expensive or generic

