## Idea 3: Developer Tooling / Claude Code Extensions

**Market Context:** MCP (Model Context Protocol) is the "USB-C for AI agents" - and marketplaces are emerging.

> Source: [MCP Market](https://mcpmarket.com/), [Claude Marketplaces](https://claudemarketplaces.com/)

### A. Premium Claude Code Plugin Pack

**Concept:** Curated, high-quality Claude Code plugins/skills sold as a bundle.

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | Medium |
| Effort | Low (leverage existing work) |
| Revenue | $29-99 one-time or $9/mo |
| Moat | Quality + curation |

**You Already Have:**
- Custom skills in `.claude/skills/`
- Slash commands
- Subagent configurations
- This could be productized

**Potential Bundle Contents:**
- Code review skill (cross-framework)
- Feature development workflow
- Design system skill
- Tech debt analyzer
- Debug-like-expert methodology
- Planning templates

### B. MCP Server for Specific Integrations

**Concept:** Build MCP servers that connect Claude to underserved tools/platforms.

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | Medium |
| Effort | Medium |
| Revenue | $19-49/mo per server |
| Moat | First-mover on specific integrations |

**Underserved Integration Ideas:**
- Golf course management systems (proprietary APIs)
- Fantasy sports platforms beyond Yahoo
- Local business tools (ServiceTitan, Jobber)
- Niche CRMs (golf industry specific)

