## Idea 6: AI Chatbot Builder for Small Businesses

**Market Context:** "No-code chatbot builders" is one of the top micro SaaS opportunities. Businesses want 24/7 automated support without technical skills.

> Source: [Microns](https://www.microns.io/blog/best-micro-saas-ideas)

### Concept: Simple FAQ Bot Builder

| Factor | Assessment |
|--------|------------|
| Viability | High |
| Effort | Medium |
| Revenue | $29-99/mo |
| Moat | Simplicity + specific verticals |

**Differentiation:**
- Focus on specific industries (golf courses, senior services)
- Pre-built templates for common questions
- Integration with booking systems
- Human handoff when bot can't help

**Why Not Intercom/Drift?**
- Those are $100+/mo minimum
- Overwhelming for small businesses
- Generic, not industry-specific

